   - Per-item modifiers (cursed +50%, high enchantment ≥5 +30%)
   - Policy-wide modifiers (first insurance +10%, loyalty -20% if ≥2 years, follow-up -15%)
   - Building blocks: exactly 3 alike components = 60 G base
   - Claim processing: deductible 100 G per damage, cap 2× insurance sum
   - High-enchantment claim clause (≥8 → 50% reimbursement)
   - Dragon material → full reimbursement (50% rule wins when both apply)
   - Rounding in MHPCO favor (premiums up, payouts down)

